cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.GR 

The paper focuses on generating, predicting, and completing human action videos using deep learning techniques. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. The paper also involves the use of optimization techniques (cs.AI) and deals with multimedia (cs.MM) and graphics (cs.GR) applications.
